  <brief_title>Efficacy of Gabapentin in Prevention of Tourniquet Pain and Hypertension</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy of Gabapentin in Prevention of Tourniquet Pain and Hypertension During Orif of Tibia Fracture Under General Anesthesia</official_title>
  <sponsors>
